INSERT INTO `wp_postmeta` VALUES (193,37,'_aviaLayoutBuilderCleanData','[av_slideshow_accordion slide_type=\'image-based\' link=\'category,9\' items=\'5\' offset=\'0\' size=\'featured\' title=\'active\' autoplay=\'false\' interval=\'5\']\r\n[av_slide_accordion id=\'353\' title=\'Dynamic Engineering Simulation\' link=\'page,80\' link_target=\'\'][/av_slide_accordion]\r\n[av_slide_accordion id=\'358\' title=\'Operator Training Simulator\' link=\'page,82\' link_target=\'\'][/av_slide_accordion]\r\n[av_slide_accordion id=\'359\' title=\'Production Management Simulator\' link=\'page,84\' link_target=\'\'][/av_slide_accordion]\r\n[av_slide_accordion id=\'357\' title=\'Dynamic Simulation Studies\' link=\'page,218\' link_target=\'\'][/av_slide_accordion]\r\n[av_slide_accordion id=\'356\' title=\'Simulator System Support\' link=\'page,220\' link_target=\'\'][/av_slide_accordion]\r\n[/av_slideshow_accordion]\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=\'invisible\' height=\'50\' shadow=\'no-shadow\' position=\'center\' custom_border=\'av-border-thin\' custom_width=\'50px\' custom_border_color=\'\' custom_margin_top=\'30px\' custom_margin_bottom=\'30px\' icon_select=\'yes\' custom_icon_color=\'\' icon=\'ue808\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth first][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth]\r\n[av_image src=\'/wp-content/uploads/qobo/2014/12/Dynamic-Engineering-Simulator220x220.jpg\' attachment=\'318\' attachment_size=\'full\' align=\'center\' animation=\'no-animation\' link=\'\' target=\'\' styling=\'\' caption=\'\' font_size=\'\' appearance=\'\'][/av_image]\r\n[/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_two_fifth]\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\n<strong>Dynamic Engineering Simulator</strong>\r\n\r\nThe HyperionRSI simulator has time and again proven to be an exceptionally powerful tool in a variety of key operational areas, including operator training and knowledge transfer, engineering studies for operational improvements and de-bottlenecking projects. With our solutions and services, we enable our customers to...\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a title=\"Dynamic Engineering Simulator\" href=\"http://localhost:8000/solutions/dynamic-engineering-simulator/\">Read More</a></p>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n[/av_two_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=\'invisible\' height=\'50\' shadow=\'no-shadow\' position=\'center\' custom_border=\'av-border-thin\' custom_width=\'50px\' custom_border_color=\'\' custom_margin_top=\'30px\' custom_margin_bottom=\'30px\' icon_select=\'yes\' custom_icon_color=\'\' icon=\'ue808\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth first][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth]\r\n[av_image src=\'/wp-content/uploads/qobo/2014/12/Operator-Training-Simulator220x220.jpg\' attachment=\'320\' attachment_size=\'full\' align=\'center\' animation=\'no-animation\' link=\'\' target=\'\' styling=\'\' caption=\'\' font_size=\'\' appearance=\'\'][/av_image]\r\n[/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_two_fifth]\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\n<strong>Operator Training Simulator</strong>\r\n\r\nPlant operators need to train for their work. Similar to the case with pilots and aircrafts, using the actual plant or plant unit as a training tool, is highly costly and dangerous.\r\nProviding a cost effective, safe, and efficient solution, we custom build high-fidelity, real-time simulators to match the dynamic behavior of single or multiple plant units...\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a title=\"Operator Training Simulator\" href=\"http://localhost:8000/solutions/operator-training-simulator/\">Read More</a></p>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n[/av_two_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=\'invisible\' height=\'50\' shadow=\'no-shadow\' position=\'center\' custom_border=\'av-border-thin\' custom_width=\'50px\' custom_border_color=\'\' custom_margin_top=\'30px\' custom_margin_bottom=\'30px\' icon_select=\'yes\' custom_icon_color=\'\' icon=\'ue808\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth first][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth]\r\n[av_image src=\'/wp-content/uploads/qobo/2014/12/Production-Management-Simulator220x220.jpg\' attachment=\'337\' attachment_size=\'full\' align=\'center\' animation=\'no-animation\' link=\'\' target=\'\' styling=\'\' caption=\'\' font_size=\'\' appearance=\'\'][/av_image]\r\n[/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_two_fifth]\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\n<strong>Production Management Simulator</strong>\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur...\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a title=\"Production Management Simulator\" href=\"http://localhost:8000/solutions/production-management-simulator/\">Read More</a></p>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n[/av_two_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=\'invisible\' height=\'50\' shadow=\'no-shadow\' position=\'center\' custom_border=\'av-border-thin\' custom_width=\'50px\' custom_border_color=\'\' custom_margin_top=\'30px\' custom_margin_bottom=\'30px\' icon_select=\'yes\' custom_icon_color=\'\' icon=\'ue808\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth first][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth]\r\n[av_image src=\'/wp-content/uploads/qobo/2014/12/Dynamic-Simulation-Studies220x220.jpg\' attachment=\'319\' attachment_size=\'full\' align=\'center\' animation=\'no-animation\' link=\'\' target=\'\' styling=\'\' caption=\'\' font_size=\'\' appearance=\'\'][/av_image]\r\n[/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_two_fifth]\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\n<strong>Dynamic Simulation Studies</strong>\r\n\r\nWith one of the largest process modeling and simulation engineering groups in the world, with expertise on several industry-standard modeling software platforms, we supply our customers with state-of-the-art simulation studies.\r\n\r\nOur customers are both end-user process manufacturers as well as leading engineering and construction (EPC) firms which build units and plants for them...\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a title=\"Dynamic Simulation Studies\" href=\"http://localhost:8000/solutions/dynamic-simulation-studies/\">Read More</a></p>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n[/av_two_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=\'invisible\' height=\'50\' shadow=\'no-shadow\' position=\'center\' custom_border=\'av-border-thin\' custom_width=\'50px\' custom_border_color=\'\' custom_margin_top=\'30px\' custom_margin_bottom=\'30px\' icon_select=\'yes\' custom_icon_color=\'\' icon=\'ue808\' font=\'entypo-fontello\']\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth first][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth]\r\n[av_image src=\'/wp-content/uploads/qobo/2014/12/Simulator-System-Support220x220.jpg\' attachment=\'321\' attachment_size=\'full\' align=\'center\' animation=\'no-animation\' link=\'\' target=\'\' styling=\'\' caption=\'\' font_size=\'\' appearance=\'\'][/av_image]\r\n[/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_two_fifth]\r\n[av_textblock size=\'\' font_color=\'\' color=\'\']\r\n<strong>Simulator System Support</strong>\r\n\r\nThroughout the life-cycle of a plant, modifications to the process or control system are being made to optimize operations. To ensure that maximum value is obtained from using a training simulator it is important that the simulators are continually updated to reflect the process and control changes...\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a title=\"Dynamic Simulation Studies\" href=\"http://localhost:8000/solutions/dynamic-simulation-studies/\">Read More</a></p>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n[/av_two_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_hr class=\'invisible\' height=\'50\' shadow=\'no-shadow\' position=\'center\' custom_border=\'av-border-thin\' custom_width=\'50px\' custom_border_color=\'\' custom_