INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (74,1,'2014-12-11 12:18:24','2014-12-11 10:18:24','<strong>RSI and Hyperion Systems Engineering change the global OTS landscape by joining forces to create HyperionRSI Simulation</strong>\r\n\r\nHyperionRSI Simulation is a company jointly owned by Hyperion Systems Engineering Ltd and RSI, delivering  Operator Training Simulator and Dynamic Simulation solutions to the global market, based on the IndissPlus simulation technology.\r\n\r\nHyperionRSI Simulation combines the experienced simulation specialists from Hyperion Systems Engineering, with the proven capability of the IndissPlus dynamic simulation technology increasing the market coverage and capabilities of the RSI Group to create the world’s largest automation-independent supplier of simulator systems.\r\n\r\nWith nearly 3 man-centuries of simulation experience and deployed from 5 locations in Cyprus, Athens, Moscow, Al-Khobar, and Pune, the company’s prime geographical focus are the markets of the Russian Federation and CIS, the Gulf Cooperation Countries (GCC), India, Greece, Cyprus and Turkey, for which HyperionRSI  is the exclusive direct supplier of IndissPlus solutions.\r\n\r\n[av_one_half first]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/qobo/2014/12/HYPERION-SYSTEMS-ENGINEERING-logo.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-393\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/qobo/2014/12/HYPERION-SYSTEMS-ENGINEERING-logo.png\" alt=\"HYPERION-SYSTEMS-ENGINEERING-logo\" width=\"250\" height=\"104\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Hyperion Systems Engineering</strong> is a provider of consulting &amp; advisory, as well as professional implementation and support services of technology based solutions to process manufacturers. With more than 20 years of experience in the Upstream Oil &amp; Gas, Petroleum Refining &amp; Petrochemicals, Chemical, and Power industries, Hyperion enables its customers to reduce operating and supply chain costs, improve safety and increase their overall profitability, always cognisant of environmental impact.\r\n\r\nHyperion Systems Engineering Ltd. is a company incorporated under the laws of Cyprus and is a group holding company with registered subsidiaries in Greece, China, Russia, Saudi Arabia, Bahrain, India, United Kingdom and the United States of America. Hyperion is certified to the ISO 9001:2008 standard, is reviewed by TRACE International and is accredited with the Investors in People Standard.\r\n\r\nFor more information, visit <a href=\"http://www.hyperionsystems.net\">www.hyperionsystems.net</a>\r\n\r\n[/av_one_half]\r\n\r\n[av_one_half]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"/wp-content/uploads/qobo/2014/12/logo-RSI-pantone1525.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-392\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/qobo/2014/12/logo-RSI-pantone1525.png\" alt=\"logo-RSI-pantone1525\" width=\"250\" height=\"104\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>RSI</strong> is a dynamic simulation solution provider with over 40 years of experience dedicated to the oil &amp; gas industry.\r\n\r\nRSI has successfully delivered more than 2000 models in more than 60 countries for major clients in the Upstream, Refining and Petrochemical Industries. From process design to plant operation, our dynamic simulation solutions, based on our proprietary technology, have been used for engineering studies, operator training and operations support.\r\n\r\nRSI is a company incorporated under the laws of France with headquarters located in Grenoble (France) and affiliates in Houston, Eatontown (USA), Beijing and Xian (China). RSI is a fully owned affiliate of IFP Training. RSI is certified ISO 9001.\r\n\r\nFor more information, visit <a href=\"http://www.simulationRSI.com\">www.simulationRSI.com</a>\r\n\r\n[/av_one_half]','About','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2014-12-24 14:29:13','2014-12-24 12:29:13','',66,'http://localhost:8000/?page_id=74',1,'page','',0);
