INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (341,2,'2014-12-24 11:03:03','2014-12-24 09:03:03','HyperionRSI Simulation is using software products that allow steady-state and dynamic analysis, both online and offline, for standard and tailor-made projects.\r\n\r\nIndissPlus is a unique software platform for simulation and control processes. At the top of its class, IndissPlus has been steadily enhanced through its application by most demanding clients while rapidly becoming a standard package for the industry.\r\n\r\n<strong>IndissPlus</strong>\r\n\r\nIndissPlus is a new approach for simulation which provides a unique environment to encompass the whole set of disciplines and related simulation tools used in the process simulation for a consolidated analysis.\r\n\r\nIndissPlus is a simulation tool for accurate examination of plant design and operation. Initially used at the design phase it is capable of hosting additional modules as the project moves from a rough initial estimate to a more precise design and further on to operation.\r\n\r\nSupporting main Standards of the domain and coming with extended interoperability features, IndissPlus seamlessly integrates any third party simulation package. IndissPlus streams a consistent set of fluid information by sharing the same thermodynamic data and methods.\r\n\r\nFor additional information on IndissPlus please visit <a href=\"http://www.simulationrsi.com/spip.php?article16\">http://www.simulationrsi.com/spip.php?article16</a>','Process Simulation Software','','inherit','open','open','','235-revision-v1','','','2014-12-24 11:03:03','2014-12-24 09:03:03','',235,'http://localhost:8000/2014/12/24/235-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (342,2,'2014-12-24 11:03:40','2014-12-24 09:03:40','The use of advanced process modeling technology as part of an ISO-certified project methodology allows efficient deployment of dynamic simulation solutions. These factors allow HyperionRSI Simulation to develop high fidelity, rigorous models in an efficient and cost-effective approach.\r\n\r\nOur dynamic simulator models are based on a combination of technologies that deliver highly accurate real-time representations of plant behavior.\r\n\r\nOTS systems can be developed and delivered for both Emulated and Stimulated (direct connect) solutions for the Distributed Control System (DCS) and Emergency Shut Down (ESD) sections of the Operator Training Simulator.\r\n\r\nOur OTS solutions represent the best-in-class combination of technology, experience and methodology. The solutions are based on proven leading-edge commercially accepted technology, which offer OTS systems with extensive capabilities.','OTS Technology','','inherit','open','open','','237-revision-v1','','','2014-12-24 11:03:40','2014-12-24 09:03:40','',237,'http://localhost:8000/2014/12/24/237-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
